---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  lang="en"
  altUrl="/es/sobre-mi/"
  title="About · José Luis Alba"
  description="Senior data engineer in Panama. 13 years across banking, insurance and retail: SAP BW, risk data warehousing, IFRS 9 in PySpark."
  activeNav="about"
>
  <section class="wrap page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Draft — being verified</p>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm a senior data engineer based in Panama, working remotely since 2013 across banking,
        insurance and retail. My work sits where a wrong number has real consequences: risk
        reporting, regulatory calculations, systems that survive a core-platform replacement.
      </p>
      <p>
        Retail — supporting a regional rollout across multiple countries on SAP BW. Banking — a risk
        data warehouse carried through a core-banking migration, and an IFRS 9 expected-loss
        calculation rebuilt in PySpark. [Cifra concreta pendiente de Sportline]. [Cifra concreta
        pendiente de IFRS 9].
      </p>
      <p>
        Today I split my time between client work and my own product — this site is where I write
        down the decisions behind both.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page {
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--orange);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .prose {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-80);
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }
</style>
